728314f-a.title: Richmond: Amboy Road - Bethel Avenue
728314f-a.text:
(1)
Amboy Road, at the N.E. corner of Bethel Ave., showing the
Bethel Methodist Episcopal Church. It stands within Bethel
4ametery. The view is westward.
1924.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
A view of the church from the opposite direction.
1924.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(3)
The same, another view.
P. L. Sperr
